      "created_at": "2025-06-20T07:39:41.803Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Yes, exactly, this is perfect unless it is too much to remember, meaning different targets on different slopes.  In which case you can also do old school and just use top tube sticker <img src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/images/emoji/twitter/slight_smile.png?v=12\" title=\":slight_smile:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":slight_smile:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></p>",
